WEBVTT

01:01:09.582 --> 01:01:12.835
A Single Drop of Dew From Dewping.

01:01:13.586 --> 01:01:15.588
Ah, I see.

01:01:16.589 --> 01:01:20.593
Good job, guys. Let's see each other again soon. Take care.

01:01:20.593 --> 01:01:26.599
Eclipseping... Just what are you scheming?

01:01:34.607 --> 01:01:37.610
Oh my, the water is all gone.

01:01:48.579 --> 01:01:53.584
You're all droopy. You poor thing.

01:01:53.584 --> 01:01:57.588
I'll cheer you up. Cheer up, Dew!

01:02:04.595 --> 01:02:10.601
Ouch, ouch, my back. This nerve pain just won't go away.

01:02:11.602 --> 01:02:14.605
Where does it hurt, Dew? Cheer up, Dew!

01:02:15.606 --> 01:02:18.609
Ouch, my back... Huh!?

01:02:18.609 --> 01:02:27.618
Haha, heave-ho! This is nothing! Spin around, spin around!

01:02:28.619 --> 01:02:32.582
Hold on a little longer. We're almost at the hospital.

01:02:33.583 --> 01:02:36.586
Cheer up, Dew!

01:02:41.591 --> 01:02:48.598
Huh? Yellow! Are you really okay?

01:02:50.600 --> 01:02:54.604
I'm glad they cheered up, Dew.

01:02:55.605 --> 01:03:00.610
Where should I spend the night tonight?

01:03:07.617 --> 01:03:10.620
It's a flower I've never seen before.

01:03:11.579 --> 01:03:15.583
This child, it's dying.

01:03:15.583 --> 01:03:19.587
I'll give you strength right away, Dew!

01:03:35.603 --> 01:03:37.188
Oh no, Dew!

01:03:45.613 --> 01:03:52.620
Phew... Thank you. I survived thanks to you, Dew.

01:03:52.620 --> 01:03:57.583
But... not a single drop of dew is left...

01:03:57.583 --> 01:04:03.047
I'll gather some dew and come back tomorrow, so please hold on until then, Dew.

01:04:07.969 --> 01:04:11.597
Yes, that's exactly it.

01:04:12.598 --> 01:04:16.602
Romi! Wake up! You're going to be late, chu!

01:04:17.603 --> 01:04:26.946
Ahhhh!!!

01:04:27.613 --> 01:04:32.618
I'm completely exhausted. Let's hurry home and lie down.

01:04:32.618 --> 01:04:37.582
No! Your book report homework! You've only written one page, chu!

01:04:37.582 --> 01:04:42.587
Oh right... Ah... I'm so tired...

01:04:42.587 --> 01:04:47.592
It would be nice if Dewping were here at times like this, poni.

01:04:47.592 --> 01:04:49.594
Dewping?

01:04:49.594 --> 01:04:55.600
There's a Princess of the Flower Kingdom who loves flowers very much, poni.

01:04:55.600 --> 01:05:01.606
If you drink the dew she gives, you get so much energy you can practice dancing all night without a problem.

01:05:01.606 --> 01:05:04.609
That's exactly what I need right now!

01:05:04.609 --> 01:05:07.612
Alright, let's go find Dewping right away!

01:05:08.613 --> 01:05:15.620
Even if Dewping is here, it's hard to get it right away, poni. You have to wait all night for the morning dew to form.

01:05:15.620 --> 01:05:21.584
That's right. Among them, there's a very special dew, and that is...

01:05:23.586 --> 01:05:27.590
It's a Teenieping alarm, chu!

01:05:29.592 --> 01:05:32.595
Huh? This is a flower shop?

01:05:32.595 --> 01:05:35.598
Let's hurry and go, guys!

01:05:42.605 --> 01:05:47.610
What? Why is he so full of energy?

01:05:49.612 --> 01:05:54.617
I gathered a lot of dew overnight, Dew.

01:05:58.329 --> 01:06:02.583
That child is... the Princess of the Flower Kingdom I mentioned earlier, Dewping, poni.

01:06:02.583 --> 01:06:07.088
That man from just now must have drunk the dew Dewping gave him!

01:06:09.590 --> 01:06:13.594
Now I can give that friend some dew too, Dew.

01:06:13.594 --> 01:06:14.595
Dewping!

01:06:14.595 --> 01:06:18.599
You're... the Princess I saw on the train?

01:06:18.599 --> 01:06:21.602
The Royal Teeniepings are here too, Dew.

01:06:21.602 --> 01:06:25.606
Dewping, come with us.

01:06:25.606 --> 01:06:27.608
Then see you later, Dew.

01:06:27.608 --> 01:06:31.612
Dewping! Wait a minute!

01:06:31.612 --> 01:06:36.283
Why are you chasing me? I don't have time to wait, Dew!

01:06:37.618 --> 01:06:39.620
Bonnyping, let's transform first!

01:06:39.620 --> 01:06:40.579
Yeah!

01:06:40.579 --> 01:06:43.582
Open, Princess Pact!

01:06:48.587 --> 01:06:54.593
Confident and bold, Bonnyping time!

01:06:54.593 --> 01:06:59.598
Princess of confidence sprouting in the heart, Princess Bonita!

01:07:00.599 --> 01:07:04.603
Dewping, stop right there!

01:07:04.603 --> 01:07:06.605
Now is not the time for this, Dew!

01:07:14.613 --> 01:07:17.616
Dewping, stop right there!

01:07:19.618 --> 01:07:21.579
I have to hurry, Dew.

01:07:25.875 --> 01:07:32.590
You waited a long time, didn't you, Dew? Just wait a little bit. I'll make you bloom right away.

01:07:32.590 --> 01:07:36.594
Cheer up, Dew!

01:07:36.594 --> 01:07:41.599
Huh? Why is it still the same? Dew? Dew!

01:07:43.601 --> 01:07:47.605
Could it be... I'm too late, Dew?

01:07:49.607 --> 01:07:58.783
Do you want to save that child? Then, give it this. It will surely bloom a beautiful flower.

01:08:03.579 --> 01:08:07.416
If I have this... this child too...

01:08:27.603 --> 01:08:29.814
Achoo! Achoo!

01:08:30.940 --> 01:08:32.608
Over here! Dewping!

01:08:32.608 --> 01:08:37.613
Achoo! Don't come closer, Dew! Achoo!

01:08:41.325 --> 01:08:45.704
Achoo! Why is my nose tickling, poni?

01:08:46.664 --> 01:08:48.332
Over there... Sapp-un!

01:08:51.043 --> 01:08:55.422
Why is there so much pollen... Achoo!

01:08:56.131 --> 01:09:05.099
Did you do this, Dewping? No, I just... I just wanted to save that child, Dew!

01:09:08.102 --> 01:09:17.611
Mwahahaha! Look at that dirty and ridiculous sight. How dare you send such things to my castle? You should suffer once too! Hahahaha!

01:09:17.611 --> 01:09:23.617
First... Achoo! Let's get out... Achoo! Out of here, Achoo!

01:09:23.617 --> 01:09:30.583
No. If we just leave it, it'll spread beyond the alley. Then the townspeople will be in danger too.

01:09:42.469 --> 01:09:45.431
Then, we'll have to first get rid of it.

01:09:47.933 --> 01:09:50.936
Wait! No! That child did nothing wrong!

01:09:50.936 --> 01:09:53.606
I'll do something about it, Dew. Achoo!

01:09:53.606 --> 01:10:03.324
I'll do something about it, Dew. How could you? Please... trust me, the Princess of the Flower Kingdom, just this once, Dew.

01:10:06.619 --> 01:10:10.873
I'll trust you. But, you have to be careful.

01:10:12.583 --> 01:10:16.587
Dew... Achoo... Achoo...

01:10:16.587 --> 01:10:19.590
Healing Dew!

01:10:30.601 --> 01:10:35.189
The pollen is too strong, so Graceping's magic is useless too.

01:10:47.326 --> 01:10:49.328
The last drop.

01:10:51.246 --> 01:10:59.797
If this continues, we'll have to get rid of you. I don't want to do that, Dew. Please... come back.

01:10:59.797 --> 01:11:03.592
Dew!

01:11:07.513 --> 01:11:09.515
That light is...

01:11:22.778 --> 01:11:24.697
It's a success!

01:11:38.544 --> 01:11:42.840
Dewping's sincere tears bloomed a real flower!

01:11:42.840 --> 01:11:48.595
The dew with the most mysterious power... that is Dewping's tears, poni.

01:11:48.595 --> 01:12:00.524
So this is your true form. It's really beautiful, Dew. Dewping, I'm glad I could confirm your beautiful heart.

01:12:00.524 --> 01:12:03.318
Will you come with us now?

01:12:03.318 --> 01:12:04.820
Okay, Dew!

01:12:05.863 --> 01:12:07.406
Piripiri Catchling!

01:12:11.577 --> 01:12:13.412
Into the Princess Cube!

01:12:21.587 --> 01:12:24.590
Princess Teenieping, Dewping, catch!

01:12:24.590 --> 01:12:28.594
The flower in my heart has bloomed brightly too, Dew!

01:12:29.595 --> 01:12:38.604
I heard a voice earlier, Dew. That voice said it could save the flower and gave me something. When I gave it to the flower, suddenly...

01:12:38.604 --> 01:12:44.610
You heard a voice? Eclipseping...!